{"tid":1302822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急! 反DQ! 用自己email send 意見書!!! 生產器出嘅不受理","createTime":"2019-07-10T05:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T01:42:42.000Z","uid":161990,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"551b0e51fa2360572f22a432c37797117bae617c","tid":1302822,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"選舉事務處做緊既朋友同我反映，<br />\n話收到5萬封email去信反DQ，<br />\n然而從下面巴打整出黎既生產器出既email address<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一律不受理</span></span>! <br />\n而對家今日已經用好多自己email及fax送出多份支持DQ意見書上去!<br />\n<br />\n希望幫手話俾大家知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要用自己email send多次，最後今日! 要快!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV?fbclid=IwAR0-sx6ipQt_H2tRX2TOFTB0mFahtN42Lp3Sqm-JpTG9mN8SoR5hTpHYaes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F271467.typeform.com%2Fto%2FMTUjKV%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-sx6ipQt_H2tRX2TOFTB0mFahtN42Lp3Sqm-JpTG9mN8SoR5hTpHYaes&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=d1eb6322\" target=\"_blank\">https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV?fbclid=IwAR0-sx6ipQt_H2tRX2TOFTB0mFahtN42Lp3Sqm-JpTG9mN8SoR5hTpHYaes</a>"},{"pid":"d0a73490f9c91eba7572826c1a8cf67fbe30667b","tid":1302822,"uid":170426,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n幫推<br />\nSend呀！！！！"},{"pid":"d766d1e8a7c2b16dfb5e8829344b8e570abde90d","tid":1302822,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"[唔好齋填form] 今日最後，一人一email 寄信去選舉會!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢度都有另一範本可用"},{"pid":"8acb0b0f72d876e666b77867483ddc4fb84ae23f","tid":1302822,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8522b66837ec5607efb046992ae719e0b71a6919","tid":13